query:
-- Get the Stickers category ID
SET @category_id = (SELECT id FROM productCategories WHERE slug = 'stickers');

-- Add the three new sticker products
INSERT INTO products (categoryId, name, slug, description, price, imageUrl, isDigital, inventory, isActive)
VALUES 
  (@category_id, 'Mountain High Vibes Sticker', 'mountain-high-vibes-sticker', 'Get those mountain high vibes with this adventurous hiking sticker! Features a cool character with backpack and walking stick exploring the great outdoors. Perfect for hikers, outdoor enthusiasts, and anyone who loves mountain adventures. Durable weatherproof vinyl!', 500, 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663233691307/oOxBLOCfzzztkYrC.jpg', 0, 100, 1),
  (@category_id, 'The Vibe Is Better When It''s Wetter Sticker', 'vibe-better-wetter-sticker', 'The ultimate paddleboard meditation sticker! Features a zen character meditating on a paddleboard surrounded by waves. Perfect reminder that the vibe really is better when you''re on the water. Great for paddleboards, water bottles, and laptops. Waterproof construction!', 500, 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663233691307/NhFXKwStCDNfmMOb.jpg', 0, 100, 1),
  (@category_id, 'Just Chillin Sticker', 'just-chillin-sticker', 'Winter paddleboard vibes! This unique sticker features a cool character meditating on a paddleboard in a snowy mountain scene. Perfect for year-round paddleboard enthusiasts who know that chill vibes transcend seasons. Weatherproof and durable!', 500, 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663233691307/IcugBuGvpRcCYzeD.jpg', 0, 100, 1)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name=name;
